Project Name: django-project
User defined apps: blog, users

users-
    register -> create a new author.
    login -> the author can log in and gets the access to published 
    logout -> the author can logout from his account.
    change password -> the user can also change the password with this utility.

blog - 
    home, about -> basic website.
    create post -> helps in creating post with header image set.
                    header image gets its caption text on its own.
    delete post -> helps in deleting the created post.